{"name":"Skillful Stare","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You successfully @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.2u915NdUyQan6uKF]{Demoralize}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Dt6B1slsBy8ipJu9]{Disarm}, @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Grapple]{Grapple}, @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Feint]{Feint}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.XMcnh4cSI32tljXa]{Hide}, @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Shove]{Shove}, @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Sneak]{Sneak}, @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Trip]{Trip}, or @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Tumble Through]{Tumble Through}. Your GM might allow you to include other skill actions in this list.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You cast @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-spells.u4Ih2CmDoHCdONpO]{Mesmerist Stare} against the target of the triggering action. If you critically succeeded, your spell attack roll and spell DC for this spell gain a +1 circumstance bonus.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"skillful-stare","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":2},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"mesmerist stare"},{"value":"a Stare"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685867888379,"modifiedTime":1685982930310,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"4MJm5bg72t8KBXvp"}
