{"name":"Circle of Resilience","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>During your daily preparations, you can designate up to 4 allies with a range of 30 feet to be in your Circle of Resilience. Once before your next daily preparations, each member of your Circle can elect to use your Will save modifier in place of their own on a Will saving throw. If an ally critically fails while using your modifier, you become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.e1XGnhKNSQIm5IXg]{Stupefied 1} for 1 minute.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"circle-of-resilience","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":18},"traits":{"value":["fortune","hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685860734011,"modifiedTime":1685978294948,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"5gLXDA6xjTCcOU3e"}
{"name":"Manifold Mesmerist","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You learn any combination of three new Cues, Stares, or Treatments. You must already know the associated spell.</p>\n<p><strong>Special </strong>You can take this feat multiple times. Each time, select three more options.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"manifold-mesmerist","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":12},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":null,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"implant cue, mesmerist stare, or touch treatment"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685982397086,"modifiedTime":1685985650118,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"7NPRLHdplSMVk2XU"}
{"name":"Master of Minds","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>When a target rolls a failure on a saving throw against one of your enchantment or illusion effects, they get a critical failure, instead. This overrides other effects that replace a failure with a success. When you roll a success on an enchantment or illusion effect against a target, you get a critical success, instead.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[{"adjustment":{"success":"one-degree-better"},"key":"AdjustDegreeOfSuccess","selector":["skill-check","spell-attack-roll"],"type":"skill","predicate":[{"or":["enchantment","illusion"]}]}],"slug":"master-of-minds","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":18},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685860734011,"modifiedTime":1685862169541,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"7kK0eONEdEKOBJLA"}
