{"name":"Scathing Spell","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You enhance your spell with antagonism, causing barely audible echoes to berate the target. If the next action you use is to cast a non-cantrip spell that deals damage to a single target, the spell deals additional persistent mental damage equal to the spell level, in addition to its other effects. This has no effect if the spell already deals persistent mental damage. The spell gains the mental trait.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"scathing-spell","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":6},"traits":{"value":["mental","hb_mesmerist","metamagic"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actions":{"value":1},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685978075448,"modifiedTime":1685980792994,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"C1hLY0GmLKx81r5F"}
