{"name":"Dreamlands or Leng","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Granted Spells</strong>: 1st @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.pBevG6bSQOiyflev]{Befuddle}, 3rd @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.sRfSBHWHdbIa0aGc]{Chilling Darkness}, 5th @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.YtesyvfAIwXOqISq]{Moon Frenzy}, 7th @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.IHUs4qn27RrdFQ5Y]{Cosmic Form}</p>\n<p><strong>Stare</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-spells.pVNZuX80Ou7c2EC0]{Slumbering Stare}</p>\n<p><strong>Planar Essence</strong>: You learn the location of each mind within 60 feet. This is an imprecise sense.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"dreamlands-or-leng","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":1},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"classfeature","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685771107381,"modifiedTime":1685862005784,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"CgFQZ79BXOVNppSk"}
{"name":"Planar Connection","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You draw your magic from a plane that your mind is intrinsically connected to. Choose one of the following planes as your planar connection. You learn the listed Cue, Stare, or Treatment, and add each granted spell to your repertoire as an occult spell when you gain this spell level. If your knack and your planar connection grant you the same 1st- level Cue, Stare, or Treatment, you may choose another. You gain the planar essence benefit if you take the Planar Essence mesmerist class feat.</p>\n<p>Planar Connections can be found here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.LMipwdeZwdk2LM1Z]{Abaddon, Abyss, or Hell}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.ibJUF0jII7fEu0AT]{Astral Plane}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.qenB2iBxX2idh6Wb]{Axis}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.QnCErGLJUgulH5Hx]{Dimension of Time or Ethereal Plane}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.CgFQZ79BXOVNppSk]{Dreamlands or Leng}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.w5untdq2QAyLV3OB]{Elysium, Heaven, or Nirvana}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.5c2x5AF16fuyVqTd]{First World or Positive Energy Plane}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.LPiwHHhIumEdke3n]{Maelstrom}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.LRz5gEMrdHWHgvLL]{Material Plane}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.YwYeXiM34ke5E6j6]{Plane of Air, Earth, Fire, or Water}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.Vt4EHMJTMMatL1NQ]{Plane of Shadow or Negative Energy Plane}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.SbscFrVHpf4NnQ4y]{The Boneyard}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.QrhVSaC7GYsh726a]{The Dark Tapestry}</li>\n</ul>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[{"adjustName":false,"allowedDrops":{"label":"level 1 mesmerist class feature","predicate":["item:level:1","item:trait:hb_mesmerist","item:type:feature"]},"choices":[{"value":"Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.LMipwdeZwdk2LM1Z"},{"value":"Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.ibJUF0jII7fEu0AT"},{"value":"Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.qenB2iBxX2idh6Wb"},{"value":"Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.QnCErGLJUgulH5Hx"},{"value":"Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.CgFQZ79BXOVNppSk"},{"value":"Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.w5untdq2QAyLV3OB"},{"value":"Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.5c2x5AF16fuyVqTd"},{"value":"Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.LPiwHHhIumEdke3n"},{"value":"Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.LRz5gEMrdHWHgvLL"},{"value":"Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.YwYeXiM34ke5E6j6"},{"value":"Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.Vt4EHMJTMMatL1NQ"},{"value":"Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.SbscFrVHpf4NnQ4y"},{"value":"Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.QrhVSaC7GYsh726a"}],"flag":"mesmeristPlane","key":"ChoiceSet","prompt":"Choose plane as planar connection"},{"key":"GrantItem","allowDuplicate":false,"uuid":"{item|flags.pf2e.rulesSelections.mesmeristPlane}"}],"slug":"planar-connection","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":1},