{"name":"Mental Rush","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>A creature critically fails at a Will save against one of your spells.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You gain temporary Hit Point equal to the creature’s level (minimum 1). If they critically failed against an incapacitation effect, double this number. These temporary Hit Points last until the creature falls @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.fBnFDH2MTzgFijKf]{Unconscious}.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"mental-rush","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":2},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685867888379,"modifiedTime":1685869762110,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"Fae7redBn8rK7huj"}
{"name":"Bespell Ego","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Frequency </strong>once per turn </p>\n<p><strong>Requirements </strong>Your most recent action was to cast a non-cantrip spell or use a Boost for one of your Stares.</p>\n<p><strong>Grants </strong>@UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-effects.mmSCpic8zX8Befpo]{Effect: Bespell Ego}</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You siphon the residual energy from the last spell you cast or Boost you used into your mind. Until the end of your turn, your spells that deal damage deal an extra 1d6 damage of a type depending on the school of the spell you just cast.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Abjuration </strong>force damage</li>\n<li><strong>Conjuration </strong>or <strong>Transmutation </strong>the same type as the next spell you cast</li>\n<li><strong>Divination</strong>, <strong>Enchantment</strong>, or <strong>Illusion </strong>mental damage</li>\n<li><strong>Evocation </strong>a type the triggering spell dealt, or force damage if the triggering spell didn't deal damage</li>\n<li><strong>Necromancy </strong>negative damage\n<p> </p>\n</li>\n</ul>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"bespell-ego","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":4},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"free"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null,"frequency":{"max":1,"per":"round"}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685978058989,"modifiedTime":1685981489396,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"H19ck1WBPfRJxnFT"}
{"name":"Frightening Hypnotism","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>You critically succeed at a check using your knack skill during a skill action</p>\n<p><strong>Duration </strong>until the end of your next turn </p>\n<hr />\n<p>The targets of the skill action become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.TkIyaNPgTZFBCCuh]{Dazzled}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.AJh5ex99aV6VTggg]{Flat-Footed}, or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened 1}, at your choice. They become immune to your @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.Hf1bejLEQM0ISZQl]{Frightening Hypnotism} for 1 hour.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"frightening-hypnotism","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":6},"traits":{"value":["emotion","fear","mental","hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Basic Hypnotism"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685978075448,"modifiedTime":1685980813949,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"Hf1bejLEQM0ISZQl"}
{"name":"Thrill of Victory","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>A creature critically fails a Will save against one of your spells.</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency </strong>once per day </p>\n<hr />\n<p>You regain one Focus Point.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"thrill-of-victory","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":1},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"free"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null,"frequency":{"max":1,"per":"day"}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685860734011,"modifiedTime":1685981438947,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"Hk9BO385jz4FmkDU"}
{"name":"Delver","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You probe others’ minds to find lost memories, or perhaps keep them hidden.</p>\n<p><strong>Treatment</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-spells.GTx5T8DMvGIjTBtD]{Memory Catalog}</p>\n<p><strong>Skill</strong>: any one skill used to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.1OagaWtBpVXExToo]{Recall Knowledge}</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"delver","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2023-06-03T09:36:00.290+04:00","version":{"schema":0.84,"foundry":"10.291","system":"4.12.7"}}},"level":{"value":1},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"classfeature","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685770436155,"modifiedTime":1685861831404,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"HoLcOjHYOlpPnfKJ"}
{"name":"Enhanced Familiar","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You infuse your familiar with additional magical energy.</p>\n<p>You can select four familiar or master abilities each day, instead of two.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[{"key":"ActiveEffectLike","mode":"upgrade","path":"system.attributes.familiarAbilities.value","priority":9,"value":4}],"slug":"enhanced-familiar","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":2},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"a familiar"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685867888379,"modifiedTime":1685869762108,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"IwKfsZb40nypv21u"}
{"name":"Silent Spell","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You’ve learned how to cast many of your spells without speaking the words of power you would normally need to provide. If the next action you use is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.aBQ8ajvEBByv45yz]{Casting a Spell} that has a verbal component and at least one other component, you can remove the verbal component. This makes the spell quieter and allows you to cast it in areas where sound can’t carry. However, the spell still has visual manifestations, so this doesn’t make the spell any less obvious to someone who sees you casting it. When you use @UUID[Item.cBInd7UusmsXOZ4H]{Silent Spell}, you can choose to gain the benefits of @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.NPM23g17n3IhdQC1]{Conceal Spell}, and you don’t need to attempt a Deception check because the spell has no verbal components.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"silent-spell","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":4},"traits":{"value":["concentrate","hb_mesmerist","metamagic"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actions":{"value":1},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Conceal Spell"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685978058989,"modifiedTime":1685980130513,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"J1RrVc7d5lZfRm9W"}
{"name":"Eyebiter","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You pluck out your eye familiar. While your eye is out of its socket, you take a -1 circumstance penalty to vision- based Perception checks, but you can see through your familiar’s vision as normal. You can use this action again to return your eye to its socket.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-effects.tEumlHvk0MEhkBe6]{Effect: Eyebiter}</p>\n<p><strong>Special </strong>When you first gain this feat, choose one of your eyes to become your familiar.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"eyebiter","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":2},"traits":{"value":["manipulate","hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actions":{"value":1},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685867888379,"modifiedTime":1685869800112,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"JanhHBMoPSiLu8Vp"}
{"name":"Steady Spellcasting","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>Confident in your technique, you don't easily lose your concentration when you @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.aBQ8ajvEBByv45yz]{Cast a Spell}. If a reaction would disrupt your spellcasting action, attempt a @Check[type:flat|dc:15]. If you succeed, your action isn't disrupted.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"steady-spellcasting","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":6},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685978075448,"modifiedTime":1685980792995,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"LGOtqcx69HIbydf3"}
{"name":"Abaddon, Abyss, or Hell","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Granted Spells</strong>: 1st @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.wdA52JJnsuQWeyqz]{Harm}, 3rd @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.sRfSBHWHdbIa0aGc]{Chilling Darkness}, 5th @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.MlpbeZ61Euhl0d60]{Cloudkill}, 7th @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.0jadeyQIItIuRgeH]{Eclipse Burst}</p>\n<p><strong>Cue</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-spells.L212rNqNIwlKiCjk]{Implanted Lie}</p>\n<p><strong>Planar <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:var(--font-size-14)\">Essence</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:var(--font-size-14)\">: You expend one of your spell slots to cast a 1-action @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.wdA52JJnsuQWeyqz]{Harm} spell at that spell level.</span></p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"abaddon-abyss-or-hell","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":1},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"classfeature","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685771107381,"modifiedTime":1685983992348,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"LMipwdeZwdk2LM1Z"}
{"name":"Maelstrom","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Granted Spells</strong>: 1st @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.gfPjmG6Fe6D3MFjl]{Pest Form}, 5th @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.d9sBzPOXX3KT8uTu]{Grisly Growths}, 6th @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.dN8QBNuTiaBHCKUe]{Baleful Polymorph}, 8th @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.8AMvNVOUEtxBCDvJ]{Monstrosity Form}</p>\n<p><strong>Stare</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-spells.HAUVrCPdQMufdsGs]{Second Thoughts}</p>\n<p><strong>Planar Essence</strong>: You inflict a @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.bestiary-family-ability-glossary.HKFoOZZV4WdjkeeJ]{Protean Warpwave} on a target creature within 30 feet. They become immune to this effect for 24 hours.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"maelstrom","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":1},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"classfeature","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685771107381,"modifiedTime":1685862122006,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"LPiwHHhIumEdke3n"}
{"name":"Material Plane","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Granted Spells</strong>: 1st @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Rn2LkoSq1XhLsODV]{Pummeling Rubble}, 2nd @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.v4KzRPol5XQOOmk0]{Heat Metal}, 3rd @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.vh1RpbWfqdNC4L3P]{Meld into Stone}, 4th @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.piMJO6aYeDJbrhEo]{Solid Fog}</p>\n<p><strong>Treatment</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-spells.pbVuNPK0NZnsaTij]{Compensating Senses}</p>\n<p><strong>Planar Essence</strong>: You call forth physical matter to form a shield. You cast @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.TVKNbcgTee19PXZR]{Shield} heightened as usual but without the 10-minute restriction on casting the spell again after using Shield Block.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"material-plane","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":1},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"classfeature","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685771107381,"modifiedTime":1685862042811,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"LRz5gEMrdHWHgvLL"}
{"name":"Undead Mastery","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>Your mesmerism reaches into the remnants of the dead’s memories. Undead are not immune to your emotion and mental effects.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"undead-mastery","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":8},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Spirit Walker"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685978089954,"modifiedTime":1685981244775,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"LWd1Dapgc5SMu8pt"}
{"name":"Thought Eater","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>You reduce a target to 0 HP with nonlethal damage. The target must be your Size or one Size smaller.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You take on the target’s form and absorb some of their mental characteristics. As long as you don’t need to take specific actions to convince others that you are the target (such as answering specific questions about their childhood or performing a complex task they specifically trained for), you automatically succeed at Impersonating the target. When you do need to make a Deception check to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.AJstokjdG6iDjVjE]{Impersonate} them, you gain a +4 circumstance bonus and, if you’re untrained in Deception, you add your level to the check as a proficiency bonus. Additionally, you can use any of the target’s @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.1OagaWtBpVXExToo]{Recall Knowledge} skills as though you were trained in them, and gain a +1 circumstance bonus when attempting to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.1OagaWtBpVXExToo]{Recall Knowledge} with them.</p>\n<p>You can dismiss this effect with a single action with the concentrate trait. This effect also ends if the target dies.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"thought-eater","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":2},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist","polymorph","transmutation"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685867888379,"modifiedTime":1685869762124,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"LlPIyC1wBcfrdrBh"}
{"name":"Quickened Casting","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Frequency </strong>once per day</p>\n<hr />\n<p>If your next action is to cast a mesmerist cantrip or a mesmerist spell that is at least 2 levels lower than the highest level mesmerist spell you can cast, reduce the number of actions to cast it by 1 (minimum 1 action).</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"quickened-casting","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":10},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"free"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null,"frequency":{"max":1,"per":"day"}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685978104404,"modifiedTime":1685982237227,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"MOu5YlduwiH5aAJx"}
{"name":"Cantrip Expansion","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>The powers of your mind have expanded. Add two occult cantrips to your spell repertoire.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"cantrip-expansion","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":2},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"a spell repertoire"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685867888379,"modifiedTime":1685869762099,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"MW3I2B6xzK9ShsqW"}
{"name":"Switch Stare","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Requirement </strong>A target is currently suffering from one of your Stares.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.AjLSHZSWQ90exdLo]{Dismiss} @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-spells.u4Ih2CmDoHCdONpO]{Mesmerist Stare} against a target. If your next action is to cast @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-spells.u4Ih2CmDoHCdONpO]{Mesmerist Stare} against the same target, they take a -1 circumstance  penalty to their save against it.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"switch-stare","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":6},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist","metamagic"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"free"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"mesmerist stare"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685978075448,"modifiedTime":1685980792995,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"MgZ0zKwjZ22GQYer"}
{"name":"Cue Conservation","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>You activate a Cue.</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements </strong>You have a Focus Point.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You spend a Focus Point to retain the triggering Cue within the target’s mind after it activates. You can then activate it again later as usual.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"cue-conservation","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":2},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"implant cue"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685867888379,"modifiedTime":1685981458443,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"Myfrdi3klMWn5e3z"}
{"name":"Conceal Spell","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>Hiding your gestures and incantations within other speech and movement, you attempt to conceal the fact that you are @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.aBQ8ajvEBByv45yz]{Casting a Spell}. If the next action you use is to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.aBQ8ajvEBByv45yz]{Cast a Spell}, attempt a Stealth check against one or more observers’ Perception DCs; if the spell has verbal components, you must also attempt a Deception check against the observers’ Perception DC. If you succeed at your check (or checks) against an observer’s DC, that observer doesn’t notice you’re casting a spell, even though material, somatic, and verbal components are usually noticeable and spells normally have sensory manifestations that would make spellcasting obvious to those nearby. This ability hides only the spell’s spellcasting actions and manifestations, not its effects, so an observer might still see a ray streak out from you or see you vanish into thin air.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"conceal-spell","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":2},"traits":{"value":["concentrate","manipulate","hb_mesmerist","metamagic"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actions":{"value":1},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685867888379,"modifiedTime":1685869762104,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"NPM23g17n3IhdQC1"}
{"name":"Reach Spell","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You can extend the range of your spells. If the next action you use is to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.aBQ8ajvEBByv45yz]{Cast a Spell} that has a range, increase that spell’s range by 30 feet. As is standard for increasing spell ranges, if the spell normally has a range of touch, you extend its range to 30 feet.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"reach-spell","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":1},"traits":{"value":["concentrate","hb_mesmerist","metamagic"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actions":{"value":1},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685860734011,"modifiedTime":1685867704294,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"OCYFrlHTeXiLYxgZ"}
{"name":"New Cue","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You learn a new Cue, of a level up to half your level rounded up. Increase the number of Focus Points in your focus pool by 1.</p>\n<p><strong>Special </strong>You can take this feat again. Each time, choose a new Cue.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[{"key":"ActiveEffectLike","mode":"add","path":"system.resources.focus.max","value":1}],"slug":"new-cue","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":1},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":null,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"implant cue"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685860734011,"modifiedTime":1685985623628,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"P6bs7jBCCOtdzdcw"}
{"name":"Mental Conduit","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>Your inborn magical nature lets you redirect ambient energies to fuel your spells. If your next action is to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.aBQ8ajvEBByv45yz]{Cast a Spell} of 5th level or lower that has no duration, you don’t expend the spell’s slot when you cast it.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"mental-conduit","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":20},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist","metamagic"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actions":{"value":1},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null,"frequency":{"max":1,"per":"PT1M"}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685860734011,"modifiedTime":1685862160859,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"PAOr9zpd8yuyg79q"}
{"name":"Phobic Insight","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You attempt to learn a creature’s deepest fear. Choose a creature you can see. Attempt a Deception, Intimidaiton, or Perception check against the higher of the target’s Deception DC or Will DC. Regardless of the outcome, the creature becomes permanently immune to your @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.PiZZ295vvLpvQMiS]{Phobic Insight}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> If the creature has a weakness to a type of damage, you learn their weakness with the highest value; in the case of a tie, your GM chooses one randomly. If the creature has no weaknesses, your GM chooses randomly between acid, cold, electricity, fire, poison, or sonic. When this creature takes the type of damage you learned about, they become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Success </strong>As critical success, but the target attempts a Will save against your spell DC each time they take this damage. On a success, they still become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened} but the effects of your @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-featfeatures.PiZZ295vvLpvQMiS]{Phobic Insight} end for them.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"phobic-insight","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":1},"traits":{"value":["concentrate","mental","hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actions":{"value":1},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685860734011,"modifiedTime":1685867743425,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"PiZZ295vvLpvQMiS"}
{"name":"Dimension of Time or Ethereal Plane","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Granted Spells</strong>: 1st @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.TTwOKGqmZeKSyNMH]{Feather Fall}, 2nd @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.4YnON9JHYqtLzccu]{Summon Animal}, 5th @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.kghwmH3tQjMIhdH1]{Summon Dragon}, 6th @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.29ytKctjg7qSW2ff]{Summon Fiend}</p>\n<p><strong>Cue</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-spells.EuS64npavig5COUM]{Deny Gravity}</p>\n<p><strong>Planar Essence</strong>: You learn the location of each mind within 60 feet. This is an imprecise sense.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"dimension-of-time-or-ethereal-plane","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":1},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"classfeature","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685771107381,"modifiedTime":1685861998062,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"QnCErGLJUgulH5Hx"}
{"name":"The Dark Tapestry","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Granted Spells</strong>: 1st @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.aEM2cttJ2eYcLssW]{Fleet Step}, 2nd @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.0qaqksrGGDj74HXE]{Glitterdust}, 5th @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.MlpbeZ61Euhl0d60]{Cloudkill}, 9th @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.ihbRf964JDXztcy3]{Disjunction}</p>\n<p><strong>Cue</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-spells.GiQiYdrFZASRwx8e]{Fearsome Visage}</p>\n<p><strong>Planar Essence</strong>: You bring the power of the void within yourself. Attempt to counteract one emotion effect affecting you. Regardless of the outcome, you can’t use this ability to attempt to counteract the same emotion effect for 24 hours.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"the-dark-tapestry","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":1},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"classfeature","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685771107381,"modifiedTime":1685862083613,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"QrhVSaC7GYsh726a"}
{"name":"Arcane Commands","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You add @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Yk3t4ekEiFIoEz9c]{Power Word Blind}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.7PJSqUeKxTqOVrPk]{Power Word Stun}, and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.m3lcOFm400lQCUps]{Power Word Kill} to your spell repertoire as occult spells. For you, these are occult spells.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"arcane-commands","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":18},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"uncommon"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685860734011,"modifiedTime":1685862169541,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"RZiUFfY9Um82ooA1"}
