{"name":"Sight Stealer","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>Once per day, your eye familiar can cast @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.VosLNn2M8S7JH67D]{Blindness} with a range of touch heightened to half your level rounded up. If you are @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.VosLNn2M8S7JH67D]{Blindness} when a creature fails their saving throw against this casting of @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.VosLNn2M8S7JH67D]{Blindness}, you recover from the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.VosLNn2M8S7JH67D]{Blindness} condition.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"sight-stealer","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":14},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Eyebiter"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685983258531,"modifiedTime":1685983602766,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"YZAFNP9Gh32cwBxD"}
{"name":"Plane of Air, Earth, Fire, or Water","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Granted Spells</strong>: 1st one of @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.y6rAdMK6EFlV6U0t]{Burning Hands} (for Plane of Fire), @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.g8QqHpv2CWDwmIm1]{Gust of Wind} (for Plane of Air), @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.jfVCuOpzC6mUrf6f]{Hydraulic Push} (for Plane of Water), or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Rn2LkoSq1XhLsODV]{Pummeling Rubble} (for Plane of Earth), 2nd @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Fr58LDSrbndgld9n]{Resist Energy}, 3rd @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.lpT6LotUaQPfinjj]{Summon Elemental}</p>\n<p><strong>Treatment</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-spells.3kG0yVthCzkwouwj]{Endure Energy}</p>\n<p><strong>Planar Essence</strong>: You cast @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.O9w7r4BKgPogYDDe]{Produce Flame} twice, heightened to half your level rounded up. It deals damage based on your planar connection: bludgeoning for the Plane of Earth or the Plane of Water, fire for the Plane of Fire, and slashing for the Plane of Air. The spell loses the fire trait and gains the associated element trait, instead.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"plane-of-air-earth-fire-or-water","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":1},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"classfeature","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685771107381,"modifiedTime":1685862048398,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"YwYeXiM34ke5E6j6"}
