{"name":"Astral Plane","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Granted Spells</strong>: 1st @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.pBevG6bSQOiyflev]{Befuddle}, 3rd @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.3x6eUCm17n6ROzUa]{Crisis of Faith}, 7th @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.WG91Z5TiR6oO5FOw]{Contingency}, 8th @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.KtTGLbLG9nqMbUYL]{Divine Inspiration}</p>\n<p><strong>Cue</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-mind-spells.qhQkVUc6yqKp6bCW]{Assured}</p>\n<p><strong>Planar Essence</strong>: Attempt to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.2u915NdUyQan6uKF]{Demoralize} a target. If you’re untrained in Intimidation, you are considered trained for this action. You gain a +2 status bonus on the Intimidation check, and you treat a success as a critical success.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic - Frontiers of the Mind"},"rules":[],"slug":"astral-plane","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":1},"traits":{"value":["hb_mesmerist"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"classfeature","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685771107381,"modifiedTime":1685861984937,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"ibJUF0jII7fEu0AT"}
